  "title": "Assistant Floor Manager, Bar (up to $3500)",
  "description": "<p>Duties:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Greet customers warmly and provide excellent service at the bar area.</li>\n  <li>Take and process drink and food orders accurately and promptly.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and serve alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverages in line with company standards.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and organization of the bar, tables, and service areas.</li>\n  <li>Monitor customer behavior to ensure a safe and enjoyable environment.</li>\n  <li>Restock bar inventory, including glasses, garnishes, and supplies.</li>\n  <li>Support bartenders and other team members to ensure smooth bar operations.</li>\n  <li>Comply with all food safety, hygiene, and liquor regulations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirement:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Previous experience in F&amp;B or hospitality is preferred (training provided for entry-level).</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and customer service skills.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment with attention to detail.</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude, teamwork spirit, and willingness to learn.</li>\n  <li>Flexible to work on weekends, evenings, and public holidays.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested applicants please WhatsApp to Wa.me/6590100921</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Toh Jun Xian</p>\n<p>Senior Consultant</p>\n<p>R1879771</p>\n<p>Revup Proservices Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA.24C2366</p>\n<p><br></p>",
